Notebook[{
Cell["OEIS Package: Benchmark", "Title"],

Cell["\<\
Real, captured timings from a single run of Benchmarks/Benchmark.wls -- not \
illustrative. Network-bound operations depend on the OEIS server and \
connection, so treat absolute numbers as indicative; the relative shape \
(pure/local-formula operations are essentially free; network calls dominate) \
is the useful takeaway.\
\>", "Text"],

Cell["$Version: 11.2.0 for Linux x86 (64-bit) (September 11, 2017)", "Text"],

Cell["Results", "Section"],

